question: Dear students, We regret to inform you that the online course registration amendment system is temporarily unavailable. However, we have provided an alternative process for students who need to make changes to their course registration for Semester I, 2023/2024 Session.
answer: Please follow these steps: 1. Get the course registration amendment form from either your faculty academic office or download it from the following link: https://amd.utm.my/files/2020/07/Borang-Pembetulan-Kursus.pdf 2. Complete the form and obtain the relevant signatures. 3. Submit the completed form to your Faculty Academic Office.
